OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774469469
OL,3,CFive people injured after building
OL,4,Ccollapses in town centre
OL,6,FFive people have been injured after a
OL,7,Fbuilding collapsed in Oldham town
OL,8,Fcentre.
OL,10,FA large cordon is in place and police
OL,11,Fand fire crews in attendance in the
OL,12,FKing Street area of the town, after
OL,13,Fthe incident, which happened at
OL,14,F12:40pm on 24 March 2026.
OL,16,FFirefighters said five people left the
OL,17,Fbuilding before emergency services
OL,18,Farrived.
OL,20,FNorth West Ambulance Service said in a
OL,21,Fstatement on X:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
