OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774469469
OL,3,CFive people injured after building
OL,4,Ccollapses in town centre
OL,6,F"Following an emergency call at 12.30,
OL,7,Fmultiple resources have attended the
OL,8,Fscene, including our Hazardous Area
OL,9,FResponse Team, Air Ambulance, doctors,
OL,10,Fadvanced clinicians and operational
OL,11,Fcommanders.
OL,13,F"Five patients have been assessed so
OL,14,Ffar, with two already taken to the
OL,15,Fhospital with injuries not believed to
OL,16,Fbe life-threatening."
OL,18,FGreater Manchester Police said: "We
OL,19,Fare currently responding to a partial
OL,20,Fbuilding collapse on King Street,
OL,21,FOldham.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1774469469
OL,3,CFive people injured after building
OL,4,Ccollapses in town centre
OL,6,F"Officers are on scene with other
OL,7,Femergency services working together to
OL,8,Fensure the safety of the public
OL,10,F"Five people have injuries at this
OL,11,Ftime that are not deemed to be life-
OL,12,Fthreatening or life-changing and
OL,13,Fsearches are continuing.
OL,15,F"A number of road closures are in
OL,16,Fplace and we would ask people avoid
OL,17,Fthe area where possible."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
