OL,3,CFive people injured after building
OL,4,Ccollapses in town centre
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService also released a statement: "At
OL,8,Faround 12.40pm this afternoon (Tuesday
OL,9,F24 March), three fire engines from
OL,10,Facross Greater Manchester were called
OL,11,Fto an incident involving a collapsed
OL,12,Fbuilding on King Street, Oldham.
OL,14,F"Firefighters are working alongside
OL,15,FGreater Manchester Police and North
OL,16,FWest Ambulance Service to make the
OL,17,Farea safe.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
